$ Javascript/CSS: show styles of a given element

The following example demonstrates how value → development/web/CSS/properties[CSS property] value from a → development/web/HTML/tags[HTML element] can be determined with
→ development/languages/JavaScript[JavaScript]: it prints all CSS property values of the document's → development/web/HTML/tags/html[`<html>`] and → development/web/HTML/tags/body[`<body>`] elements. If these value differ, the values are printed in red.

